data.description: Beautifully updated and well maintained home with an above-ground pool! This gorgeous home features spacious living areas, and an inviting primary bedroom and en-suite highlight this home! Updates include a roughly 3-year-old roof, brand new siding, windows and doors, and a HVAC and Water Heater that were replaced in the last 5 years. Relax in your own pool in your own private backyard, or work in the spacious garage on projects, this home has something for everyone! Conveniently located in Norfolk only a few minutes from the Naval Base, Downtown, Zoo, Harbor Park, and so much more! Don't miss out on this perfect blend of comfort and entertainment! Schedule your showing today!!
